## viewport.js
a 2D camera (viewport) designed to work with PIXI.js

## Code Example

    // create a renderer
    renderer = new Renderer({color: 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)'});

    // create the viewport
    var viewport = new Viewport(renderer, 1000, 1000);

    // move the center
    viewport.moveTo(500, 500);

    // zoom in
    viewport.zoom(500);

## Installation

    npm install yy-viewport

